CatDescriptText: Ms. Elaine Coles, executive administrative assistant at the Urban League of Pittsburgh from 1960 to 1996, poses in a living room.  She is wearing a semi-formal plaid skirt, velvet top, and shawl.  According to the sitter, she was on her way out to a special event, and the date was c. 1954.
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Elaine Coles wearing plaid skirt, halter shirt, and knit shaw, posed with hands on hips looking into mirror, with Christmas decoration on table in foreground
